                "\n" +
                "Laurelai scanned the horizon in all directions circling slowly to the right, until she’d seen everything the world had to show her, but nothing stood out until she came full circle and found an angel standing there with his sword to her throat.\n" +
                "\n" +
                "“I haven’t found you yet, but I will,” he rasped as she realized who the strong man was. This was the angel that she had raped at the monastery. “It’s your fault too. I can’t get you out of my mind.”\n" +
                "\n" +
